Jaws is here! 

Here is Jaws! 

(He is a shark without a cause) 

He was in a movie, you should watch it it's called Jaws 

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

A shark-based SCP that I decided to use as the debut for the Supplementary Classification System. For those interested,  means the creature has physical effects. (As opposed to, for example, mental/sensory effects.)

The idea for this one is based off of something my dad told me a while back. Basically, his parents took him to see Jaws when he was about 6 years old, and it scared the crap out of him. He started thinking that the shark was everywhere, not just in the ocean, but in the pool, and even in his toilet. I thought that it'd be a fun thing to turn into a skip. Also, it gives me an excuse to link Lemon Demon's P







